@startuml
actor User
boundary ModeratePostsView
control ModerationController
entity POST

User -> ModeratePostsView : Select function get pending posts
activate ModeratePostsView
ModeratePostsView -> ModeratePostsView : Validate input information

alt Valid input
    ModeratePostsView -> ModerationController : getPendingPosts()
    activate ModerationController
    ModerationController -> POST : Query pending posts
    activate POST

    alt Posts found
        POST --> ModerationController : Posts list
        ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Success response
        ModeratePostsView --> User : Display posts list
        User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm success notification
    else No posts found
        POST --> ModerationController : Empty list
        ModerationController --> ModeratePostsView : Error response
        ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify no posts found
        User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm error notification
    end
    deactivate POST
    deactivate ModerationController
else Invalid input
    ModeratePostsView --> User : Notify invalid input
    User -> ModeratePostsView : Confirm error notification
end
deactivate ModeratePostsView
@enduml